      "text": "I'm doing well. Thank you. Hey, I just wanted to reach out to you. Um, we work with a lot of similar properties and portfolios in the area. Um, just to help so vacancies and build out call lists and wait lists. Wondering if maybe you had a few minutes to chat at some point maybe next week and see if if we might be a good fit for you guys."
